### API v1 - Reservations Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:8000

### 1. Create Reservation
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/reservations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_id": 1,
  "quantity": 2,
  "version": 0
}

### 2. Get My Reservations
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/reservations/my-reservations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Update Reservation
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/reservations/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 3,
  "version": 0
}

### 4. Cancel Reservation
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/v1/reservations/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Create Reservation - Exceed Limit (should fail)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/reservations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_id": 1,
  "quantity": 10,
  "version": 0
}
